name: This is our past
description:
I've been recollecting our past yesterday. Feel it, touch it, smell it. You were sitting there. Facing the landscape. Busy taking pictures while i kept silent and stared at my shoes. I can't seem to see the things you see. And that's the reason i came here again, to this very place, took the same picture from the position same as you. And, damn, it was beautiful.

Blok M, 2014
